    "7216607": {
        "Desc": "Listen in on the locals' conversations",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "\"Ipe\"",
                    "T": "...Oh, this? Well, the secret to fishing is patience."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ipe\"",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ipe\"",
                    "T": "No, no, it's not boring at all. I love fishing."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "He sounds like he's talking to someone."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ipe\"",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ipe\"",
                    "T": "The fish don't sing, but if you sing to them, I'm sure they can hear you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ipe\"",
                    "T": "Not that this means they wouldn't eat you too, of course!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ipe\"",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ipe\"",
                    "T": "No problem. Once you're older, I'll teach you how to fish."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ipe\"",
                    "T": "But when you grow up, you've got to teach me the secret of the Ishine Script. I mean, this is knowledge that only gets passed through the priestly families — you know, your family."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ipe\"",
                    "T": "For example, the words on those rocks..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7216653": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": []
    },
    "7216640": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": []
    },
    "7216608": {
        "Desc": "Go to Wakukau Shoal",
        "Step": "According to the locals, they need someone to help them find Ruu. This trip is starting to feel like a waste of time... But you might as well have a look around the island to see if you can find any other leads. They say that Ruu enjoys hanging out around Wakukau Shoal, Oina Beach, and the Autake Plains — First stop, Wakukau Shoal it is, then.",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wow! It appeared!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ipe\"",
                    "T": "Huh, to think that Ishine Script had this kind of power. Perhaps it's related to the ley lines in some way... How unexpected."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ipe\"",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ipe\"",
                    "T": "You're right. The previous priests did have a sense of humor, huh?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ipe\"",
                    "T": "...Why do I like fishing? Hmm, let me think about it for a moment..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ipe\"",
                    "T": "If I had to put my finger on it, it's because fishing makes me feel like this ocean and the rest of the world are connected. That way, this island doesn't feel so small, even though we can't escape the Sea of Fog."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ipe\"",
                    "T": "And... Uh, how should I say this? I guess I've also fished up all kinds of interesting stuff along the way."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ipe\"",
                    "T": "Like for example, the knowledge that you love to sing in secret."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, is he talking to Ruu?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Well, if people can talk to dragons..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Then the ability to talk to nonexistent people isn't too strange."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Th—That's true, yeah... We've really seen a lot of weird stuff while traveling together, huh?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ipe\"",
                    "T": "C'mon, it's nothing to be embarrassed about. You sing pretty well! I feel luckier just listening to you, you know?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ipe\"",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ipe\"",
                    "T": "You wanna sing for Makiri? Sure, but I mean, why d'you need to ask me?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ipe\"",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ipe\"",
                    "T": "Alright then. If you're going to Oina Beach, say hi to Kama and the others for me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ipe\"",
                    "T": "Careful now, if you get lost in the fog, just play the Maushiro. I'll come find you for sure."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
