    "7216609": {
        "Desc": "Talk to the illusions",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "Hey there."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Kama\"",
                    "T": "Oh, it's you, Ruu."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh, that's the weird \"Kama\" from before..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "Sorry to disappoint you, but I've picked every last seashell off this beach today!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Kama\"",
                    "T": "I mean, wasn't our intention to give them to him so—"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "Hey!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Kama\"",
                    "T": "Ah."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "Hehe, maybe I should say instead that you've come at just the right time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "I mean, aren't there some rocks with that... Uh, whatever you call that writing again, on them."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "I remember you saying that the order was very important, Ruu. So if we mess the rocks' order up..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Kama\"",
                    "T": "They call it the Ishine Script. I've said this before, I don't think this is a good idea."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Kama\"",
                    "T": "And Ruu's here too. I don't think he'll let us do this, considering that he's the son of the priest and all..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Kama\"",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Kama\"",
                    "T": "What? You wanna join in?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "Hah! See? I always knew Ruu wasn't some stick-in-the-mud!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "Alright then, let's do this!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "Hahaha, this is real funny, watching a future priest touch these stones just like the records say they should... and then coming up blank in the end."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Kama\"",
                    "T": "I still think this isn't right."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "Pfft, this guy's a bore. You know what? Let's not hang out with him. Let's go ruin-delving with Kito and Kina!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Kama\"",
                    "T": "Actually, Ruu, since you're pretty friendly with those two, could you remind them to please take care of themselves?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Kama\"",
                    "T": "I, too, believe that there are green lands beyond the Sea of Fog, and humans too, and that there were people and history before the Thunderbird came, but someone needs to record the things that happened in our village."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "Tch. You're such a killjoy."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "You know what, Ruu? You should grow older faster."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "If you were the priest, I'm sure you'd lead us all out of the Sea of Fog to see the outside world..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "I wonder, can I wait for that day to come?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "Ah, right. Kama said that he saw you at the Autake Plains the other day."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "You've gotta be careful over there. The fog is thickest in that area — you fall off the cliff and that's the end for you!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Kama\"",
                    "T": "Mm. If you really do have to go, take me with you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "That's right! Kama over here's got a brain like a rock, but he's no ordinary rock — he's got a sense of direction!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7216610": {
        "Desc": "Solve the mystery of the stones",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "You know, Ruu..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "Would you like to come with me?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "I'm serious! The world outside this fog really does exist!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "I've seen people come in from the outside. Once, there was someone who came to the island, lost their way in the fog, and injured themselves in a fall as a result."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "That person told me all sorts of things about the outside world. He said that he came from an island on the other side of the sea. There's no fog there — only rolling green lands, a blue sky, and a golden sun."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "He said that the Thunderbird always flies from our island to his, and it was the sight of the Thunderbird in flight that made him want to come over and see what it's like here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "I know, right? I found it really mysterious, too!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "So how about it, then? Wanna come with me? This place is just too stifling."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "Grandpa Mata isn't a bad person, but he just isn't willing to doubt our ancestors' words. But as for me, I want to go see what the outside world is like!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "Anyway, I hate the idea of offering people to the Thunderbird... And I'm sure the Thunderbird probably hates it too."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "Well, about Kama... That's true, huh. If we left him alone here..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Sayo\"",
                    "T": "But I get it. If you've decided to stay, then I'm sure this place will become a better one thanks to you!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
