    "7216706": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Kama",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "Yikes!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Uh, I didn't mean to scare you..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "You're... an outlander..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "And you've got... a little floating girl with you too! That's awesome! I haven't seen any outlanders in soooo long!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon's not a \"little girl\" or whatever. Paimon's Paimon! And who're you, kiddo?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "My name's Ruu!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "#Well, I'm {NICKNAME}."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "#I'm the legendary {NICKNAME}."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "#Ooh, the legendary {NICKNAME}?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Uh, either way, the important thing here is..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "To remind this kid to get to a safe spot."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "To ask about the whereabouts of the Maushiro."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "No, no, we've got to figure out who the \"littler\" person is here! How many years old are you, Ruu?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "Umm... What does \"years old\" mean?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "That's the number of years that've gone by since you were born."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "The number of years? Let me count..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "Several thousand, maybe! Sorry, I can't remember anything more specific."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Uh..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Um..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "How do you count \"a year,\" if I might ask?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "Hmm. A year passes whenever I hear the thunder, of course. Just like everyone counts it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Whaaaa..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "(Hold it just a minute there. Didn't Sumida say that Tsurumi Island's civilization has vanished for several millennia now?)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "(And his way of counting years is so weird!)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(It's probably because they can't see the sun or moon due to the giant fog.)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(Well, either way, let's hear what the kid has to say.)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "Still, you've come at exactly the right time! Today's the day of our big ceremony!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "Kapatcir will definitely be pleased to have new and rare guests taking part."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Who's that?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "My good friend!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "So there'll be a ceremony?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Sounds like a lot of fun!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "Exactly! Everyone tells me that I'll be the star of the show this time, too!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "But we'll need to do some things before the ceremony can start!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "#Either way, {NICKNAME}, Paimon, come with me!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7216705": {
        "Desc": "Travel to Tsurumi Island",
        "Step": "Using Kama's boat, you arrive at the mysterious, fog-shrouded island to help Sumida put her novel together. Next up, you need to go deeper into the land and retrieve this so-called Maushiro.",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wow! So this is Tsurumi Island? This..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "...Looks really sad! What's with this huge fog!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Sumida mentioned this as well."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "A most unique environmental phenomenon."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Kama, do you know that... Uh, what is it again?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "\"Kino's Travels\"?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kama",
                    "T": "Yes, Lady Sumida has mentioned it before."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "No! That's not what Paimon means! Paimon's talking about that Maushi-something that Sumida asked us to come look for!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "The Maushiro?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah! That's it!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Kama, do you know where we should start looking?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "If he knew, Sumida wouldn't need our help."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ugh, this is so annoying! Does Paimon have to do everything herself!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I think you're forgetting who does the heavy lifting around here..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "All the same, do you have any suggestions?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kama",
                    "T": "It's best to enter through that great gate over there, lest you get lost in the fog all too easily."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kama",
                    "T": "I will wait for you here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kama",
                    "T": "Look for me once you secure the Maushiro. I will send you back."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
