    "7216721": {
        "Desc": "Find your way through the mist and make an offering at the Perches",
        "Step": "The Tsurumi locals are behaving a little oddly, but you take their commission to make offerings at three perches nonetheless. As long as the ceremony goes smoothly, you should be able to get your hands on the Maushiro and complete Sumida's commission.",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh. Feels like we've gotten our bearings now, huh?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Yup, even though the fog hasn't dissipated yet."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Eh? There's a kid over there..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Do Inazuman kids all run off to deserted islands to play when they've got time on their hands?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We should tell him to get to safety."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah, and let's ask about the thing Miss Sumida asked us to get in the meantime."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We can ask if he knows anything about the Maushiro."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Great idea!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7216717": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Abe",
                    "T": "Even if it was only just once, I'd love to leave the Sea of Fog and see what lies beyond..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Una",
                    "T": "Are you an idiot? It's utter darkness out there."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Una",
                    "T": "Didn't the priest say that if we leave the fog, our souls will become lost shadows that roam the Realm of Silence beyond?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Una",
                    "T": "If it wasn't for the Great Thunderbird using the fog to protect the island, we'd have been goners long ago."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Abe",
                    "T": "I know, and that's why we hold ceremonies to thank the Great Thunderbird for its protection."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Abe",
                    "T": "...But aren't you curious about the outside world anyway?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Una",
                    "T": "There were those who tried to leave this place and follow the Great Thunderbird's light to seek new lands. None of them returned alive. You do remember the Kama family's boy, don't you, old man?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Abe",
                    "T": "Oh, how could I forget..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Abe",
                    "T": "Perhaps I simply wish that all went well with him..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
