    "7217210": {
        "Desc": "Destroy the Perches",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ruu! You're alright..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "#{NICKNAME}, Paimon..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "Why... Why did you do this?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Eh?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "I thought that the two of you were good, strong people..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "And that you'd be different from the others! You came back to look for me, listened to everything I said... I thought that the ceremony would go well this time... But..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "We want to stop the ceremony! That way, you'll be safe!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We're just trying to help."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "But you're not helping!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Why do you want the ceremony to proceed?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "Back then... Something happened. Something went wrong. Things were going so well..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "But then I woke up. I found that the island had become like this. Everyone was weird. No one could see me. No one could hear me!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "Then after a while, a storm would start, and it would be super scary. At these times, only Wakukau, Oina, and Autake wouldn't be struck by lightning. I'd hide there and wait for the storm to end."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "But once the thunder stopped, everything would repeat all over again. I would wake up — and everyone would be doing the same things."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "Kapatcir's missing, too. I couldn't find her, not even on Mt. Kanna."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "The ceremony must have gone wrong. We must've made her angry."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "That's why I prepared another ceremony, and another, and another. But it always ends the same. That's why I had the idea of bringing in people from the outside."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "I thought that... you were my friends, and that you'd help me..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Actually, hold on a moment. Who is Kapatcir, anyway?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "That's what I've been thinking, too."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "Other people call her the Thunderbird. She's our guardian deity."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "She's the Thunderbird, isn't she?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "That's right, that's what they call her. She's our guardian deity."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "If the ceremony goes smoothly, Kapatcir will be pleased. That way, everyone will be happy."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "In the past, Kapatcir paid no attention to the people who were offered to her. But I'm different..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "That's why I have to make sure that the ceremony goes well. That way, everyone can go back to normal and live their lives again."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "Big Brother Ipe and Big Sister Makiri will get married, and Kina and Kito will grow up and become great adventurers!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "And once things are better here, Big Sister Sayo will come back! Big Brother Kama, too! And Dad will no longer have to be afraid of Kapatcir's wrathful lightning!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "And everyone would realize that the outside world isn't a bad place, because there are good people like you in it..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "...So why? Why did you ruin the ceremony?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Because this isn't right!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "That's not true! This is right! Don't... Don't come back here again!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "There's going to be another storm. I—It's going to be super scary!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "Just go already! I don't want to see you ever again! *sobs*"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "No use staying here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Let's go and report back to Miss Sumida."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Mm. You're... You're right."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Let's go."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
