    "7217212": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Sumida",
                    "T": "Indulge my curiosity for a moment... Since you're a descendant of Tsurumi Island's people and your family seems quite interested in handing down their history..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sumida",
                    "T": "Would you know how to make Maushiro, by any chance, Kama?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sumida",
                    "T": "It's totally okay if you don't, by the way! It was a long time ago and all..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kama",
                    "T": "I do. My grandfather taught me how to make them — and how to use them, too."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sumida",
                    "T": "What... Uh... Then why did I spend all that Mora to hire people..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sumida",
                    "T": "*cough* So then, is there anything else you can tell me about the Maushiro?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kama",
                    "T": "They make \"bwoooom\" sounds."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sumida",
                    "T": "I—I think I already knew that. Is there anything else?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kama",
                    "T": "They are made of wood, and have no special requirements in that regard. Yumemiru Wood, Otogi Wood, they will all do."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kama",
                    "T": "Let me think, was there anything else... Ah. If you give a Maushiro you made personally to someone, that is considered a marriage proposal."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sumida",
                    "T": "What!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sumida",
                    "T": "That's not bad, actually. I'll include that into the story!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
