    "7217332": {
        "Desc": "Defeat opponents",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "Ah, it's so beautiful..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "If only I could have seen such sights together with everyone..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "Ah, but I'm happy just to be able to do it with you two!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "The world beyond the fog is amazing! I never knew the sky was so high up or so large."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "I wonder what the places Kama went to were like..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We can go see those places."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "That's right! The outside world is a reeeally big place."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "We've met lots of interesting and nice people along the way, too. You'll hit it off with them in no time!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "There's loads and loads of awesome food, too! Sweet Madames, Almond Tofu, Sticky Honey Roasts..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "Ooh! Sweet Madames sounds like they'll be great!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#That's right, we've had a ton of those in our journey, haven't we, {NICKNAME}?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ooh, yeah! We also met a certain Tone-Deaf Bard during our journey. He loves music too."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon's sure you two would be the best of friends. Maybe you'll even perform together in Mondstadt's city square!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#And... And... We can take you on adventures! {NICKNAME}'s a real ace at that! We'll go to all sorts of places, like the super high-up Wangshu Inn..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "There's also the Grand Narukami Shrine, which is way up high too, and has a big tree that looks like a kitsune! And we can go to Sangonomiya Shrine on Watatsumi Island. That place looks like something out of a dream..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "Yup, I know, and I'd love to follow you all outside as well."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "#Thank you, {NICKNAME}, Paimon."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "It's all thanks to you that I was able to fulfill my promise with Kapatcir. And... I guess everyone doesn't look all weird anymore."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "I'm sorry."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "I thought that you'd broken the Perches, and I blamed you for that... Even though you're both good people."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "It's alright! We've been on lots of adventures and got ourselves into a ton of misunderstandings. Don't take it to heart."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "And even if you don't wanna travel with us, we've got friends who'll take care of you! We know a young lady your age in Mondstadt's Knights of Favonius..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So... Please leave Tsurumi Island with us, Ruu..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "I... When we went to Seirai Island to sing for Kapatcir, I could feel that a piece of me was in that feather."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "That's why I'd like you to take that feather of hers on your travels."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "This way, I can travel with the two of you as well. We'll even bring Kapatcir with us, too!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "We'll go see the outside world, and we'll hear what songs they have to sing."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But...!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Paimon."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "Yup, you don't have to worry about me!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "It was great going outside, but it was real tiring, too..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "I'd like to rest for a bit. You can go on ahead first!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "Oh, that's right! Could you please thank Big Brother Kama for me?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Okay. Goodbye!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "Yup! Let's meet again."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "We'll definitely meet again!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
