    "7217318": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Touch",
                    "T": "Curious tunes, tiny human. Afraid not of thunder and storms?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "Eh...? Is this... the first time I met Kapatcir?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ruu\"",
                    "T": "The adults in the village all said that I can bring peace to thunder and storms."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh, this memory is clearer than before... Is that because Ruu is here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ruu\"",
                    "T": "I was too embarrassed to sing in the village, so I came here to practice!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ruu\"",
                    "T": "Do you like it? Hehe..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Touch",
                    "T": "Before you humans learned to make fire, the thundering storm had already swept across the ocean alongside me. With but a flap of my wings, purple lightning will tear through the clouds like serpents. My cry shakes the ocean depths and heart of the earth."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Touch",
                    "T": "I have heard the songs of the trees, the strains of the cloud and rain, and the melodies sung by the blue flying dragon of the far north. I have heard every trembling chorus of fox and rabbit and worm as I descended upon the land."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Touch",
                    "T": "But your song is special. It is different from that of the boar, the fish, and the Wen Kamuy."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ruu\"",
                    "T": "You're speaking all funny. I don't get it..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ruu\"",
                    "T": "But I guess you like my song, then?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Touch",
                    "T": "I do not know. I only know that I have never heard it before."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ruu\"",
                    "T": "Well, then I shall sing you another tune — when you come again with thunder and rain!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Touch",
                    "T": "Your lives are fragile and puny. Perhaps you shall already have turned to dust before I remember this matter. But if you have not, then you shall sing for me again."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ruu\"",
                    "T": "Everything you say is so complicated..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ruu\"",
                    "T": "Oh, yes! My name's Ruu. What's yours? Everyone in the village calls you \"Great Thunderbird,\" but you must have a name, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Touch",
                    "T": "A name?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ruu\"",
                    "T": "Well, that is... What should I call you? I mean, if I want to sing for you again, and I call out to you, what shall I call out?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Touch",
                    "T": "I do not know. She gave me a name long ago, but I have forgotten it. I do not need such things, nor have any dared to summon me thusly—"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ruu\"",
                    "T": "Well, how about this then? Dad... I mean, Grandpa Mata taught me a few new words in the Ishine Script today. Let me try using them to give you a name!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ruu\"",
                    "T": "Hmm... Oh! Oh, this should do!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "And so I gave her the name Kanna Kapatcir..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ruu\"",
                    "T": "Let's name you \"Kanna K{RUBY#[S]Great Eagle of the Storm}apatcir,\" then!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Touch",
                    "T": "...Ridiculous. Still, it matters not to me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ruu\"",
                    "T": "Well, it's decided, then! I need to get back now, or the adults will worry. I'll definitely sing for you again!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Touch",
                    "T": "Hah. Perhaps I shall forget you immediately, \"Ruu.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Ruu\"",
                    "T": "Well, I won't forget! See you!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
