    "7217319": {
        "Desc": "Report back to Sumida",
        "Step": "Report back to Sumida and finish your commission.",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ah, it flew away..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kama",
                    "T": "It flew off to Mt. Kanna..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "Are those... Kapatcir's memories?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "They should be."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "She always remembered you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Well, you did give her a name, after all."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "She also remembered my promise to sing for her again."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "But... But if that's the case, why did everyone become like this? Why did the village become like this?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "Did we anger Kapatcir by not performing the ceremony correctly?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I don't think that this was what the Thunderbird was mad about..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kama",
                    "T": "I see. I understand now, more or less."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kama",
                    "T": "Well then, I suppose our next stop is Mt. Kanna."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "But that's sacred ground. We can't set foot there..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "#And {NICKNAME}, Paimon, you've already come around three times, and yet things haven't gotten better..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Well, you're the one who talked about \"The Rule of Three.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "\"Good omens must occur three times for good fortune to truly descend.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "And \"You must forge past obstacles three times to succeed on the fourth.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "...You know what? Paimon still thinks this should be called the \"Rule of Four\" instead!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "*sigh* Maybe you're right, Paimon..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kama",
                    "T": "#True. You've already met with three difficulties, {NICKNAME}, Paimon."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "That we have."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "Alright. I believe you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "And since Kama... I mean, Kama's descendant has also returned, this must mean that good things are in store for us..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ruu",
                    "T": "But if nothing good happens, I'll be very, very mad, you hear?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kama",
                    "T": "Of course. Let's go, then."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
